BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260507T061200
DTEND:20260507T085400
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.866ft at 06:12\n-0.026ft at 08:54\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 SSW swell persists\, along with WNW swell\, for mainly waist-stomach high 
 surf\, while best breaks see chest-shoulder high sets. Draining mid mornin
 g negative low tide\, then incoming tide push helps through mid day. Waves
  gradually wind down during the afternoon when the swell starts to taper o
 ff. \n\nMorning winds are looking light and favorable\, followed by a ligh
 t SW sea breeze in the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
